genresAdvancedInfo.name: baltic choir
genresAdvancedInfo.description: This genre features the rich, harmonious sounds of choirs from the Baltic region. Often incorporating traditional folk elements, Baltic choir music is known for its haunting melodies and lush arrangements. From solemn hymns to joyful celebrations, this genre captures the soul of the Baltic people and their deep connection to music.
